Accepted nursing students who meet the requirements for direct entry are eligible for a $20,000 per year Need for Nursing Scholarship. Students have the opportunity to study abroad at Harlaxton college in England and still graduate in 4 years.  We offer 6 semesters of clinical experience as well as personalized learning with small class sizes.
-MnWi2l-6WzYB6fnzJh7.name: University of Evansville Dunigan Family School of Nursing

-MnWiM4tTJpbWtZjWhuh.desc: The UE Doctor of Nurse Anesthesia Practice program is a 3 year Doctoral program to train RNs to be CRNA's.  To apply, you must first complete your BSN in Nursing and have at least 18 months ICU experience.
-MnWiM4tTJpbWtZjWhuh.name: University of Evansville Nurse Anesthesia

-MnWilg_rozEgRjLMcH8.desc: The College of Nursing and Health Professions offers 12 academic programs in Dental Assisting, Dental Hygiene, Diagnostic Medical Sonography, Food and Nutrition, Health Informatics and Information Management, Health Services, Health Administration, Nursing (Bachelor of Science in Nursing, RN to BSN Completion, Master of Science in Nursing and Doctor of Nursing Practice), Occupational Therapy Assistant, Occupational Therapy, Radiologic and Imaging Sciences and Respiratory Therapy.  Our programs have an outstanding history of graduates achieving excellent pass rates on national and state licensure examinations, as well as preparing our students for employment and leadership roles in health care organizations throughout the country.
-MnWilg_rozEgRjLMcH8.name: USI - College of Nursing

-MnWj4yPNaD_XKp-mnPS.desc: At USI’s Pott College of Science, Engineering, and Education you chart a path to the future with engineering disciplines in demand all over the world.  Your interest in problem-solving and aptitude in mathematics serve you well in the pursuit of your baccalaureate degree. The first two years of course-work provide a foundation for several disciplines, including general engineering, manufacturing engineering, mechanical engineering, civil engineering, electrical engineering, and manufacturing technology.  To learn more about our program, please visit: https://www.usi.edu/science/engineering/
-MnWj4yPNaD_XKp-mnPS.name: USI - Pott College

-MnWj5biB6RPft8G5z_f.desc: Since 1859, we’ve been an independent Lutheran school with a reputation for not only incredible academics, but a bright, energetic spirit that attracts students that truly want to make a difference in this world.   At Valpo, all the wide-ranging things that define you come together. You’ll reach your full potential. And you’ll do it with our total commitment to guide you, inspire you and bring out your absolute best. Our campus defines a culture where no one is left out. And our approach to hands-on, experiential learning gets you out of the classroom and into real life.
-MnWj5biB6RPft8G5z_f.name: Valparaiso University

-MnWjZw4MPl0yHFyD_8I.desc: The goal of the Vanderburgh County Sheriff’s Office is to provide the most efficient and effective law enforcement service to the citizens of Vanderburgh County. To increase the safety of our community, we have established multiple ways for you to furnish information anonymously regarding criminal or suspicious activity. Vanderburgh County is a wonderful place to live, work, relax, and raise a family. Working together, we will keep it safe for everyone.
-MnWjZw4MPl0yHFyD_8I.name: Vanderburgh County Sheriff's Office

-MnWl-6PRuo23prXvWK-.desc: Vincennes University Architectural Studies Program and Building Information Modeling (BIM) Program.  The Architectural Studies degree leads students to working for a company as an Architectural Technician upon graduation or transferring to an accredited school of Architecture to continue their education to become an Architect.  The BIM degree is made up of courses in architecture, construction, and surveying.  This degree leads students to working for a company as a BIM Technician upon graduation or continuing their education while majoring in Building Construction Management at Vincennes University.
-MnWl-6PRuo23prXvWK-.name: Vincennes University - Architectural/BIM

-MnWlYpM3ZsCqUP0dP2w.desc: The Advanced Manufacturing Automation Technology Program degree is a 2 year Associates Degree and we offer options to continue your degree to a Bachelors Degree through Vincennes University or Purdue University. The degree concentration is in  indistrial automation including robotics programmable logic controllers and sensors. We look forward to meeting you on Career Day!
-MnWlYpM3ZsCqUP0dP2w.name: Vincennes University - Automation Technology

-MnWlrt7YsJBs4zOniRt.desc: Vincennes University Hospitality management program offers a two year degree in culinary art, pastry art, and hotel management. We offer small class sizes with lots of one on one time with the chefs. Just a short drive from Evansville. Come check us out!
-MnWlrt7YsJBs4zOniRt.name: Vincennes University - Hospitality

-MnWmIrj5dw5fA8fKByG.desc: Vincennes University Information Technology Department represents over 14 programs of study ranging from certificates, Associate Degrees, and Baccalaureate degree programs. The programs of study include Computer Science, Software Development, Cyber Security, Data Analytics and Visualization, Programming and Game Development, Web Design, Information Technology, Cyber Security and Network Operations, Networking and Security Specialist, Business Office Management Technology, and more. Our team of professors  make the curriculum  come alive through special projects and activities that give students real world work experience and innovative ways to apply student learning. All of our professors have industry experience working in the field of Information Technology.
-MnWmIrj5dw5fA8fKByG.name: Vincennes University - Information Technology

-MnWmWhMrkaf3epDWcge.desc: The Vincennes University Homeland Security and Public Safety Program leads to a four-year Bachelor of Science degree.  This program has garnered numerous national awards.
-MnWmWhMrkaf3epDWcge.name: Vincennes University - Public Safety

-MnWn10JFZGFQu95FUmG.desc: The Vincennes College of Technology offers a variety of programs in Aviation, Land Resources, Electronics, Manufacturing, and Transportation. Our dedicated faculty, with years of industry and education experience, provide students with high quality, hands-on education that prepares them for rewarding careers in high demand fields.
-MnWn10JFZGFQu95FUmG.name: Vincennes University College of Technology

-MnWnFNWxXSrAbZXKwLp.desc: The Communication Department at Vincennes University offers 2-year associate degrees in Communication and Public Relations; Communication Studies; Broadcasting; Broadcast Journalism; Journalism; and Photojournalism. Our courses are hands-on with a focus on learning by doing. We would love to meet you and talk more about these opportunities!
-MnWnFNWxXSrAbZXKwLp.name: Vincennes University Communication Department

-MnWvkHYdjHojuU8IChK.desc: Vincennes University Diesel Technology is focused on different aspects areas, we have 2 year degrees in Diesel Medium/Heavy-Duty Trucks, John Deere Ag Tech, Power Generation, Cummins TAP programs in Power Generation and Medium/Heavy-Duty Trucks , and a one year certificate in Medium/Heavy-Duty Trucks. Our Partnership with SICTC lets students take advantage of transferring in both Engines and Electrical courses.
-MnWvkHYdjHojuU8IChK.name: Vincennes University Diesel Technology

-MnWwAPCFaA3hUKjaJmt.desc: Vincennes University is proud to offer high-quality educational programs in a variety of majors.  Health career programs include Nursing, Health Information Management, Funeral Service Education, Pharmacy Technology, Surgical Technology, and Physical Therapist Assistant.
-MnWwAPCFaA3hUKjaJmt.name: Vincennes University Health Sciences

-MnWxDO8Ca955zxaGm5g.desc: The Vincennes University Legal Studies program prepares students for careers in the legal field, from paralegal to preparation for law school.  All courses are taught by licensed attorneys and give students an in-depth, hands-on look at real law courses.
-MnWxDO8Ca955zxaGm5g.name: Vincennes University Legal Studies Department

-Mnb3J_F8vnfjoyai4lU.desc: Wabash Valley College Diesel Equipment Technology Program is a two year Associate Degree program. Focus is on Ag, Heavy Equipment  and On-Highway Truck Equipment.
-Mnb3J_F8vnfjoyai4lU.name: Wabash Valley College - Diesel

-Mnb3Vk0h-lHpfS94Ppb.desc: Wabash Valley College's national award winning Radio/TV and Digital Media Department offers multiple 2-year degrees programs for students interested in careers in broadcasting. Degree options offered include Radio/TV Broadcasting,  Sports Media and Music & Media. Students gain real world experience by working at the college's radio station 89.1 The Bash and TV station News Channel 15.
-Mnb3Vk0h-lHpfS94Ppb.name: Wabash Valley College - Radio/TV

-Mnb3dfuRW0B9bYOY3gO.desc: Since 1997, WEOA has been Evansville’s ONLY urban format radio station, laying the foundation for feel-good crossover tunes and a sincere dedication to community outreach. WEOA’s exclusive loyal listeners and unique attention to the community has made it a heritage staple resting at 98.5 FM, 100.7 FM, and 1400 AM. For over two decades, we continue to be the source for Hip-Hop and R&B music.
-Mnb3dfuRW0B9bYOY3gO.name: WEOA Radio

-Mnb3tDg-RPwnsRgkiPH.desc: WNIN Tri-State Public Media, Inc. has both TV and Radio public media stations.  We also produce digital content that may be streamed on our website, viewed as a podcast, or posted on various social media channels.  WNIN is a non-profit organization that connects with the community through award winning local programming and a number of special events each year.  We hire student interns to assist our staff in many areas including TV Production, Radio, Digital/Social Media, Events, and Engineering.  Please visit our website for more information at https://www.wnin.org/.
-Mnb3tDg-RPwnsRgkiPH.name: WNIN Tri-State Public Media, Inc.
